<h4 id="redirect">Redirect</h4>

{{% choosable language csharp %}}
<dl class="resources-properties"><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Required. The value to put in the HTTP location header of the response. The location can contain capture group values from the pattern using a `:` prefix to identify the segment and an optional `*` to capture the rest of the URL. For example: "glob": "/:capture*", "statusCode": 301, "location": "https://example.com/foo/:capture"{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
